post_text:
Strength & Agility Program - STARTS TUESDAY, JULY 14th @ 8:00 a.m.

Our Strength and Agility Program was supposed to start on Monday, July 13th but due to the gym floor not being finished, we will be starting it on Tuesday, July 14th at 8:00 a.m. Corey Knutson will be there and start with baseline testing.

This is a FREE program for all female athletes going into grades 7-12 on:
Mondays @ 10:00 a.m.
Tuesdays@ 8:00 a.m. (during open gym bb)
Thursdays @ 8:00 a.m. (during open gym vb)

Thanks to the Girls Athletic Booster Club for sponsoring this program!

post_text:
We would like to pass on some information regarding the upcoming vote that is taking place for the Grand Meadow School District as there are a lot of Grand Meadow and surrounding area community members that see this page:

The Grand Meadow School district is asking voters to come to the polls on Tuesday, March 11th to decide on a 13.895 million dollar addition and renovation project. For more information, go to the school webpage and look under "District Quick Links", then click on the Referendum Information link. Please get informed and remember to vote. Tell your family members and friends to get out and vote too! (the direct link to the website is below)

http://www.gm.k12.mn.us/page/3064
